"A well-designed spreadsheet is the simplest and most flexible tracking tool available. Create columns for: company name, position title, job posting URL, date applied, application method (direct site, LinkedIn, referral, recruiter), contact person, email or phone, current status (applied, phone screen scheduled, interview scheduled, offer, rejected, no response), follow-up date, and notes.\n"
