msgid "Apply within the first 24 to 48 hours whenever possible. Data from LinkedIn and Indeed shows that applications submitted in the first two days receive significantly more attention from recruiters. Many positions receive the majority of their applications within the first week, and hiring managers may begin screening before the posting closes. Setting up job alerts ensures you see new postings as quickly as possible."
