"\n"
"Give before you ask. Share relevant articles, make introductions, congratulate contacts on achievements, and offer your expertise when it could be helpful. People are significantly more likely to help someone who has demonstrated generosity and genuine interest in the relationship. If your first outreach in five years is asking for a job referral, you have started the relationship on an imbalanced footing.\n"
