#: src/data/wiki/categories/resume-sections.ts
msgid "In most cases, a resume summary is the better choice because it highlights what you offer the employer, not what you want from them. Objective statements are considered outdated for experienced professionals. The only exception is if you are a brand-new graduate with no work experience at all, in which case a brief objective can provide direction. Even then, a skills-based summary often performs better."
msgstr "In most cases, a resume summary is the better choice because it highlights what you offer the employer, not what you want from them. Objective statements are considered outdated for experienced professionals. The only exception is if you are a brand-new graduate with no work experience at all, in which case a brief objective can provide direction. Even then, a skills-based summary often performs better."

#: src/data/wiki/categories/industry-guides.ts
msgid "In most Western countries, a photo is not recommended and may introduce bias into the hiring process. However, in some international markets, particularly in Asia and the Middle East, photos are standard practice on hospitality resumes. Research the norms of the specific market and employer you are targeting. When in doubt, omit the photo and let your qualifications speak for themselves."
msgstr "In most Western countries, a photo is not recommended and may introduce bias into the hiring process. However, in some international markets, particularly in Asia and the Middle East, photos are standard practice on hospitality resumes. Research the norms of the specific market and employer you are targeting. When in doubt, omit the photo and let your qualifications speak for themselves."

