#: src/data/wiki/categories/networking-linkedin.ts
msgid "Non-responses are common and should not be taken personally. Follow up once after five to seven business days with a brief, polite message. If there is still no response, move on. Many professionals receive dozens of messages daily and may have simply missed yours. Try reaching out through a different channel, or ask a mutual connection for an introduction. For every person who does not respond, several others will be happy to share their time and insights."
