"After your work experience, include your education section. List your degrees in reverse chronological order, including the institution name, degree type, field of study, and graduation date. If you graduated with honors or achieved a notable GPA, include that information. For professionals with more than five years of experience, the education section typically receives less emphasis than work experience.\n"
