"\n"
"Career fairs, recruitment events, and professional conferences are additional contexts where you should have copies of your resume readily available. Even in the digital age, many recruiters appreciate receiving a printed resume during face-to-face interactions. Job seekers who attend these events prepared with professional printed resumes demonstrate initiative and professionalism.\n"
